While connecting the camera the silver side of the camera plug should be towards the HDMI port on the Raspberry Pi
Step 1: Update the raspberry pi using
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get upgrade
	sudo raspi-config	#And enable Camera Option in the Interfacing Options
Step 2: Install the pycamera
	sudo apt-get install python-picamera pythin3-picamera
	OR
	python3 -m pip install picamera
